Class ErrorCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mariuszgromada.math.janetsudoku.ErrorCodes

  • public final class ErrorCodes
extends java.lang.Object
    Error codes definition for Janet-Sudoku. The code convention is as follows:
    Errors.[CLASS]_[METHOD]_[ERROR_TYPE]
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:

    mariuszgromada.org@gmail.com
